name: Joycon 3D Icons — Community File
description:
Take your designs to the next level with cheerful 3D icons!


Joycon is a 3D icon pack created in Figma, which can help you make your design more attractive. Whenever you need to illustrate something, you can use this icon pack and step away from boring flat illustrations.


This is just a free demo.

If you want to get the full pack (64 icons) click this link and secure your 3D Icon Pack before the 50% sale ends.
